                            ################
                            About Najakotiva
                            ################
@WORDWRAP

Najakotiva is a multimedia art group.  The main branch of our interest is
music, but we make video and performance as well.  We experiment with
sound.  We play computer music - from industrial tekno to minimal ambient
and we use live instruments as well:  violin, cello and drums.  We
cooperate with performers and dancers (for example Dance Theatre Nei).

Najakotiva Software is the Amiga programming team.  We write specialised
programs for Najakotiva artists.  We make them accessible to the Amiga
community as shareware, however.  midiIn is the first finished product, the
others are on various levels of developement:  Negativland - playing
animations and demo-like procedures syncronised to MIDI signals, SMPTE Box
- transferring audio SMPTE signal to MIDI Time Code and opposite, using the
Amiga standard paralell port sampler.

We hope to deliver Amiga fanatics high quality modern software.

